text: Can you hear my heartbeat? Tired of
feeling never enough. I close my eyes
and tell myself that my dreams will come
true. There'll be no more darkness when
you believe in yourself. You are
unstoppable. Where your destiny lies.
Dancing on the blades. You set my heart
on fire. Don't stop us now. The moment
of truth. We were born to make history.
We'll make it happen. We'll turn it
around. Yes, we were born to make
history.
